  "title": "Junior Technician (On Job Training)",
  "description": "<p><strong>• Salary range: $1500 - $2200</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Working hours: Monday – Friday (9:00am – 6:00pm)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Working Location at Serangoon North</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Excellent Welfare &amp; Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Well Established Medical Equipment Supplier Company</strong></p>\n<p><strong>• Training Provided</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform rehabilitation equipment setup and maintenance – including drilling and painting.</li>\n  <li>Conduct equipment quality checks at onsite and offsite locations.</li>\n  <li>Support delivery of equipment.</li>\n  <li>Perform any other maintenance duties as assigned by the Supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE O Level and above</li>\n  <li>0 – 2 years related experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
